videos.headline: Miami (OH) strikes first with diving TD
videos.description: Miami-Ohio RB Jaylon Bester dives over the line to put Miami (OH) on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Miami (OH) strikes first with diving TD) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Lazzaro sells fake to perfection on 21-yard TD run
videos.description: Central Michigan QB Tommy Lazzaro fakes out a defender with a perfect pump fake and takes the open hole to the house for a 21-yard TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Lazzaro sells fake to perfection on 21-yard TD run) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Sorenson finds open hole on screen and scores
videos.description: Miami (OH) WR Jack Sorenson turns on the jets after a short screen and all the Central Michigan defense sees is his back as he runs in a 31-yard touchdown.
